[{"Id": 1010077, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "The reverent Sayyid Ali Khan al-Shirazi, has mentioned in his book of Kalim Tayyib that Almighty Allah’s Greatest Name (Isme Aazam) stands for each statement that beings with the word “Allah” and ends up with the word “huwa (He),” provided that the statement (in Arabic) be empty of any dotted letter and that its recitation does not change whether it is parsed or not. Such statements can be found in the Qur’an in five verses of five different Surahs. Shaykh Maghribi says, “If one betakes to these five verses as a dua that is repeated 12 times a day, all his general and particular affairs will be made easy for him without delay, Allah willing.” These five verses are as follows…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Sayyid Ali Khan al-Shirazi ne apni kitaab Kalim Tayyib mein zikr kiya hai keh, Isme Aazam lafz “Allah” se shuru aur lafze “Howa” par tamaam hota hai. Is mein Ism ke huroof bila nuqte ke hai aur is par eraab lagaaye ya na lagaaye, iski qiraat mein koi farq nahi padhta aur woh Qur’an Kareem ki paanch (5) suroh ki mukhtalif aayato’n mein hai. Shaikh Maghribi ka farmaan hai keh, “jo shakhs rozana 11 martaba in aayato’n ko padhne ka apna vird bana le, to uski har chhoti badi mushkil bohot jald aasaan ho jaayegi.” Woh 5 aayaat yeh hai…", "UrduDescription": "سید اجلّ سید علی خاں شیرازی ؒ نے کتاب کلم طیب میں نقل کیا ہے کہ اسم اعظم لفظ اَللہسے شروع اور لفظ ھُوَ پر ختم ہوتاہے، اس میں اسم کے حروف بلانقطہ کے ہیں اور اس پر اعراب لگائیں یا نہ لگائیں، اس کی قرائت میں کوئی فرق نہیں پڑتا اوروہ قرآن کریم کی پانچ سورتوں یعنی سورۂ بقرہ، آل عمران، نساء، طٰہٰ اور تغابن کی پانچ آیتوں میں موجود ہے۔ شیخ مغربیؒ کافرمان ہے : جو شخص روزانہ گیارہ مرتبہ ان آیات کے پڑھنے کو اپنا ورد بنا لے تواس کی ہر چھوٹی بڑی مشکل بہت جلد آسان ہو جائے گی اور وہ پانچ آیات یہ ہیں۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "En