Text9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1003296, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 255, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Allah is He besides Whom there is no god, the Everliving, the Self-subsisting by Whom all subsist; slumber does not overtake Him nor sleep; whatever is in the heavens and whatever is in the earth is His; who is he that can intercede with Him but by His permission? He knows what is before them and what is behind them, and they cannot comprehend anything out of His knowledge except what He pleases, His knowledge extends over the heavens and the earth, and the preservation of them both tires Him not, and He is the Most High, the Great.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Allah jiske alaawa koi Khuda nahi hai zinda bhi hai aur Usi se kul kaayenaat qaayem hai Usey na neend aati hai na ongh aasmaano aur zameen mein jo kuchh bhi hai sab Usi ka hai. Kaun hai jo Uski bargah mein Uski ijaazat ke bagair sifaarish kar sake. Woh jo kuchh unke saamne hai aur jo pas'e pusht hai sab ko jaanta hai aur yeh Uske ilm ka ek hisse ka bhi ehaata (gheraaw) nahi kar sakte magar Woh jis qadr chahe. Uski kursi'e ilm o iqtedaar zameen o aasmaan se wasee-tar hai aur Usey unke tahaffuz mein koi takleef bhi nahi hoti woh aali martaba bhi hai aur saheb'e azmat bhi.", "Urdu": "اللہ جس کے علاوہ کوئی خدا نہیں ہے زندہ بھی ہے اوراسی سے کل کائنات قائم ہے اسے نہ نیند آتی ہے نہ اُونگھ آسمانوں اور زمین میں جو کچھ بھی ہے سب اسی کا ہے، کون ہے جو اس کی بارگاہ میں اس کی اجازت کے بغیر سفارش کرسکے، وہ جو کچھ ان کے سامنے ہے اور جو پسِ پشت ہے سب کوجانتا ہے اور یہ اس کے علم کے ایک حّصہ کا بھی احاطہ نہیں کرسکتے مگر وہ جس قدر چاہے، اس کی کرس علم و اقتدار زمین و آسمان سے وسیع تر ہے اور اسے ا ن کے تحفظ میں کوئی تکلیف بھی نہیں ہوتی وہ عالی مرتبہ بھی ہے اور صاحبِ عظمت بھی۔", "RArabic": "ALLAHU LAAA ILAAHA ILLAA HUWAL HAIYUL QAIYOOM; LAA TAAKHUZUHOO SINATUNW WA LAA NAWM; LAHOO MAA FISSAMAAWAATI WA MAA FIL ARD; MAN ZAL LAZEE YASHFA’U INDAHOOO ILLAA BI-IZNIH; YA’LAMU MAA BAINA AYDEEHIM WA MAA KHALFAHUM WA LAA YUHEETOONA BISHAI’IM MIN ’ILMIHEE ILLAA BIMAA SHAAA’; WASI’A KURSIYYUHUS SAMAAWAATI WAL ARDA WA LAA YA’OODUHOO HIFZUHUMAA; WA HUWAL ALIYYUL ’AZEEM.", "ArabicText1": "اَللهُ لَآ اِلٰهَ اِلَّا هُوَ اَلْحَيُّ الْقَيُّوْمُ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": "ج ", "ArabicText2": "لَا تَاْخُذُهٗ سِنَةٌ وَّلَا نَوْمٌ", "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": "ط ", "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": "لَهٗ مَا فِي السَّمٰوٰتِ وَمَا فِي الْاَرْضِ", "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": "ط ", "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": "مَنْ ذَا الَّذِيْ يَشْفَعُ عِنْدَهٗٓ اِلَّا بِاِذْنِهٖ", "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": "ط ", "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": "يَعْلَمُ مَا بَيْنَ اَيْدِيْهِمْ وَمَا خَلْفَهُمْ", "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": "ج ", "ArabicText6": "وَلَا يُحِيْطُوْنَ بِشَيْءٍ مِّنْ عِلْمِهٖٓ اِلَّا بِمَا شَاۗءَ", "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": "ج ", "ArabicText7": "وَسِعَ كُرْسِيُّهُ السَّمٰوٰتِ وَالْاَرْضَ", "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": "ج ", "ArabicText8": "وَلَا يَئُوْدُهٗ حِفْظُهُمَا", "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": "ج", "ArabicText9": "وَهُوَ الْعَلِيُّ الْعَظِيْمُ", "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": n